imdb.plot outline: Super Random Report is an entertaining & comedic take on pop & geek culture featuring the latest in technology, entertainment, and viral news. The show will cover it all with a sprinkle of comedic banter by real life friends, Sharon Apple and Arnold Basingat. These crazy kids will explore and present content ranging from comic conventions, cars, and video games to the latest in digital media. Super Random Report will also highlight Filipino Americans involved in the topics discussed and present various ways technology can affect the community.
